quran[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Iqeôb ed i medden uqeîîi nnsen, u nitni stehzan, ur d rzin"
  21,2,"Ur ten d ippas usmekti amaynut, s$uô Mass nnsen, mebla ma ppuraren, mara s sslen"
  21,3,"Ur d rzin wulawen nnsen. Ppemcawaôen wid idensen, s tuffra: \"d acu t wagi, siwa amdan am kunwi? Day a pvefôem ssêur, kunwi tepwalim"
  21,4,"Inna: \"Mass iw Iéôa timenna deg igenni, di tmurt. Neppa Issel, Issen"
  21,5,"Maca, nnan: \"d taffa n tirga. Xaîi! Isnulfa t id. Xaîi! Neppa d amedyaz. Aha san, ad a$ d iawi assekni, akken id ippuceggaâ i imezwura"
  21,6,"Ur tumin, uqbel nnsen, yal temdint Nesqucc, day ad amnen nitni"
  21,7,"Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, siwa irgazen, iwumi Nweêêa. Steqsit imawlan usmekti, ma ur teéôim"
  21,8,Ur ten Nerri d tifekkiwin ur ntepp lqut. Ur wekkôen
  21,9,"Sinna, Neîîef deg wayen i sen Nâahed, u Nsellek iten akked wid i £ ihwan. Nen$a imcumen"
  21,10,"Ih, Nessers awen ed Tazmamt, degs asmekti nnwen. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  21,11,"Acêal n temdinin idensen ay Neôéa! Nexleq, deffir sent, agdud nniven"
  21,12,"Mi êussen i lwaâôan nne£, atnan la regwlen, segs"
  21,13,"Ur regwlet ara, u$alet ar wayen is testasrem, ar ixxamen nnwen. Amar fellawen asteqsi"
  21,14,"Nnan: \"a yamxix nne$, nella, s tidep, d imednas"
  21,15,"Ur tfukk ti$ôi yagi nnsen, armi ten Nerra d aqecqac urhif"
  21,16,"Ur Nexliq ara, i wurar nne£, igenni, tamurt, akked wayen illan garasen"
  21,17,"Lemmer day Neb$i lhawiyya, yili Nebbwi p id, s $uône£, maday Naâna"
  21,18,"Xaîi! Nekkat tikerkas s tidep. Tneqq itent. Neqvent. A tawa$it nnwen, ilmend n wayen d teggarem"
  21,19,"IneS kra illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Wid illan $uôeS, ur sme$wôen ara iman nnsen, $ef uâabed iS. Ur âaggun"
  21,20,"Ppanzen iv akked wass, ur sêissifen"
  21,21,"Ne$ ddmen d, si tmurt, iôebbiten id ipparan ar ddunit"
  21,22,"Lemmer llin degsen iôebbiten, war Öebbi, war ccekk, ad fesden. Gedha s Öebbi, Mass n usgeld, seg wayen id ggaren"
  21,23,"Ur fellaS asteqsi $ef wayen Ixeddem. Nitni, fellasen asteqsi"
  21,24,"Ne$ day ddmen iôebbiten, war Neppa? Ini: \"Awit ed atebbet nnwen\". Ayagi d asmekti i wid illan yidi, d asmekti i wid illan, uqbel i. Maca, tegwti segsen, ur ssinen tidep. D$a zzin akin"
  21,25,"Ur d Nuzen amazan, uqbel ik, siwa ma Nweêêa yas ar: \"ur illi ôebbi siwa Nek, ihi âabdet iyI"
  21,26,"Nnan: \"Isâa Uênin aqcic\". Gedha s yiS! Xaîi! D imdanen imaâzuzen"
  21,27,"Ur S d zeggwiren deg wawal, xedmen s lameô iS"
  21,28,"Iéôa i illan zdat sen, akked wayen illan deffir sen. Ur ççafâan, siwa $ef win Iôuva. U nitni, si lxuf iS, pêadaren"
  21,29,"Win, segsen, id innan: \"nek d ôebbi, war Neppa\", a t Nqeîîi s Loahennama. Akka ay Nepqeîîi imednas"
  21,30,"Ne$ wid ijehlen ur walan ara tamurt akked igenwan llan mlalen? Nessemfaôaq iten, Nga s waman kra n wayen idren. Ihi, day ur ppamnen ara"
  21,31,"Nerra di tmurt idurar, iwakken ur tepêerrik ara yissen. Nerra, degsen, tiza d iberdan, amar ad pwanhun"
  21,32,"Nerra igenni d ssqef innestaôen, u nitni ooan issekniyen nne£"
  21,33,"D Neppa i Ixelqen iv akked wass, iîij akked waggur, yal wa iteddu deg ubrid is"
  21,34,"Ur Nefka ara, uqbel ik, tameddurt n lebda i umdan. Day keçç a ppemmtev, nitni ad wekkôen"
  21,35,"Yal amdan ad ijeôôeb tameppant. Nepjeôôib ikwen s cceôô, akked lxiô. D ahewwel. £uône£ tu$alin nnwen"
  21,36,"Mara k id walin wid ijehlen, pmmaâliken kan fellak: \"d wagi id ikkaten deg iôebbiten nnwen\"? Nitni nekôen asmekti n Uênin"
  21,37,"Ipwaxleq umdan si leêmeq. Ad awen d Ssenâate$ issekniyen iW, ihi, ur iyI $eûbet"
  21,38,"Qqaren: \"melmi lemâahda yagi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  21,39,"Wid ijehlen, a lemmer ad éôen tagwnip ideg ur d tekksen udmawen nnsen, ne$ iârar nnsen, si tmes! Nitni ur pwasellken"
  21,40,"Xaîi! A ten id ias, deqzalla, a ten iwwet ba$a, ur zmiren a t rren, ne$ ad gganin"
  21,41,"Ni$ ttahan $ef imazanen, uqbel ik! Ayen i$ef mmaâlken, izzi d $ef wid, segsen, i ittahan"
  21,42,"Ini: \"anwa ara kwen ifukken, iv akked wass, seg Uênin\"? Maca, ooan asmekti n Mass nnsen"
  21,43,"Ne$ sâan iôebbiten ara ten ifukken, war Nekwni? Ur zmiren ad sellken iman nnsen, ur sâin imâiwnen mgal a£"
  21,44,"Xaîi! Nestaser i wigi akked imezwura nnsen, ar tewser nnsen. Day ur walan ara, Neppas ed ar tmurt, Nessenqas si leryaf is? Day d Nitni ara irebêen"
  21,45,"Ini: \"la kwen nedôe$ kan, s uweêêi\". Ur sellen iâééugen i unabi ma ppunedôen"
  21,46,"Ma iêuza ten uûuvu uâaqeb n Mass ik, war ccekk, a d inin: \"a ssexv nne$! Ih, nella d imednas"
  21,47,"A n Nessers lmizanat iûewben, ass n tnekra. Ur ipwadnes umdan s wacemma. Xas d aâqqa ucceryad, a t id Nawi. Nesteqnaâ yisne£ i uqeîîi"
  21,48,"Ni$ Nefka i Musa akked Haôun, afraz, akked tafat d usmekti, i wid ipêezziben"
  21,49,"Wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, ur T walan, u pêaraben $ef yimir"
  21,50,"Wagi d asmekti iôqan, id Nessader. Day a t tagwim kunwi"
  21,51,"Ni$ Nefka, zik, nnhaya s i Ibôahim? Nella Nessen it"
  21,52,"Mi inna i baba s akked ugdud is: \"d acu tent tâancurin agi, i la tepkabarem"
  21,53,"Nnan d: \"Nufa d imezwura nne$ la tent âabden"
  21,54,"Inna: \"ihi, tellam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen, di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  21,55,"Nnan: \"tusiv a$ d, s tidep, ne$ keçç seg wid ippuraren"
  21,56,"Inna: \"xaîi. Mass nnwen d Mass n tmurt akked igenwan, id Ixleq. Nek, seg inagan n waya"
  21,57,"S Öebbi, ard ad andi$ i tâancuôin nnwen, mara teîîixxôem"
  21,58,"Isseftutes itent, siwa tameqwôant degsent, amar a d u$alen $uôes"
  21,59,"Nnan: \"anwa i igan akka i iôebbiten nne$? Neppa, war ccekk, d amednus"
  21,60,"Nnan: \"nesla i ileméi, itent id iudren, isem is Ibôahim"
  21,61,"Nnan: \"awit ep id, zdat wallen n medden, amar ad ilin d inagan"
  21,62,"Nnan: \"day d keçç i igan akka, i iôebbiten nne$, a Ibôahim"
  21,63,"Inna: \"xaîi, i igan akka, d ameqwôan nnsen agi. Steqsit pen, ma pmeslayen"
  21,64,"Endekwalen d. Nnan: \"ih, d kunwi ay d imednas"
  21,65,"Sinna, bran i iqweôôa nnsen: \"ni$ wigi, teéôiv, ur pmeslayen ara"
  21,66,"Inna: \"day tâabdem, war Öebbi, ayen ur kwen inefâan, ur kwen iîîuôôun, s wacemma"
  21,67,"Tfuh i kunwi, akked wayen tâabdem, war Öebbi! Day ur tefhimem ara"
  21,68,"Nnan: \"sseô$et ep, u sellket iôebbiten nnwen, ma tâazmem"
  21,69,"Nenna: \"a times, ili d tasmuvi u d talwit, i Ibôahim"
  21,70,Undin as p. Nerra ten d imexsuôen mavi
  21,71,"Nsellek it, akked Luî, ar tmurt i Neôqa i imavalen"
  21,72,"Nefka yas Isêaq, Nerna yas Yaâqub. I sin, Nerra ten d wid imaânen"
  21,73,"Nerra ten d imvebbôen, nehhun s lameô nne£. Nweêêa yasen igiten ilhan, taéallit, azekki. Llan d wid i £ iâabden"
  21,74,"I Lut, Nefka ûûwab, tamusni. Nsellek it si temdint i illan txeddem tucmitin. Llan, s tidep, d agdud n dir, d laâôuô"
  21,75,"Nesskecm it deg uêunu nne£. Neppa, ih, seg wid imaânen"
  21,76,"I Nuê, zik, mi inâaô. Njaweb as ed. Nsellek it, neppa akked twacult is, si lefqaâ abarar"
  21,77,"Neneêêel it mgal agdud i iskaddben issekniyen nne£. Llan, s tidep, d agdud n dir. Ne$ves iten meôôa"
  21,78,"I Dawed akked Sliman, mi êudden $ef yiger, ideg ksant wulli n medden. Nella d Inagan uêuddu nnsen"
  21,79,"Nessfehm as p i Sliman. I sin, Nefka ûûwab, tamusni. Nêeppem i idurar akked igvav ad sbuccâen Dawed. D ayen Newqem"
  21,80,"Nessêefv as, ad awen iûnaâ iceîîiven, ara iêarben fellawen si tiytiwin. Day a ppesnemmrem"
  21,81,"I Sliman, avu n tarikt, ipûuvu s lameô is, $er tmurt i Neôqa. Nezga Néeô yal cci"
  21,82,"Ger ccwaîen, wa i$evves as, wa iqubel cce$l nniven. Nella d imêaraben nnsen"
  21,83,"I Yub, mi inuj $eô Mass is: \"nek pwa$e$. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun"
  21,84,"Njaweb as ed. Nekkes as it ivuôôen; Nerra yas d tawacult is, akw, yides, tin i p icban. D aêunu s$uône£, d asmekti i iâabaden"
  21,85,"Ismaâil, Idris, Dulkifl, akken ma llan, d iûebôiyen"
  21,86,"Nesskecm iten deg uêunu nne£. Nitni, s tidep, seg wid imaânen"
  21,87,"I Dannun, mi iôuê s wurrif. I$il ur Nesâi ara adabu fellas. Inâaô, di tellis: \"ur illi ôebbi siwa Keçç. Gedha s yiseK! Nek lli$ si imednas"
  21,88,Njaweb as ed. Nâateq it si éémik. Akka ay Nâateq lmumnin
  21,89,"I Zakaria, mi inuj $uô Mass is: \"a Mass iw! Ur iyi Ippaooa ara d amengur. Keçç, Tifev akw iweôôaten"
  21,90,"Njaweb as ed. Nefka yas Yaêia, Nesseêla yas tameîîut is. Nitni, s tidep, izga izwar lxiô nnsen. Pnujun $uône£, s tugwdi d usirem. Unzen a£"
  21,91,"Ar tin i iqqimen zeddiget, Nûuv si ôôuê nne£. Nerra p, neppat akked mmi s, d assekni i imavalen"
  21,92,"Lois agi nnwen, war ccek, d lois yiwen. Nek d Mass nnwen, ihi âabdet iyI"
  21,93,"Gezmen lameô nnsen garasen. £uône£, akw, ara d u$alen"
  21,94,"Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan u irna iumen, ur ipôuêu laâtab is. Ih, Nekwni Nepparu fellas"
  21,95,Ipwagdel asen a d u$alen $eô temdint i Nesqucc
  21,96,"alamma serrêen d i Iaouo d Maouo. Nitni, si yal ti$ilt, a d azzlen"
  21,97,"Tqeôb ed lemâahda n tidep. Atan iqquô yiéôi n wid ijehlen: \"a tawa$it nne$! Ni$ nella ne$fel $ef waya. U, aâer, nella d imednas"
  21,98,"Kunwi, s tidep, akked wayen tâabden, war Öebbi, d is$aôen n Loahennama. £ures, kunwi, teppeddum"
  21,99,"Lemmer llin widak d iôebbiten, ur p keççmen. Akw, ad wekkôen degs"
  21,100,"I nitni, degs, zzhir. Nitni, degs, ur sellen"
  21,101,"Ma d wid iwumi izwar ssaâd, s$uône£, widak, segs, ad baâden"
  21,102,Ur sellen i ûûut is. Ad wekkôen deg wayen cihwant teôwiêin nnsen
  21,103,"Ur ten i$webbel lweêc abarar. A ten magrent lmalayek: \"assa, d ass nnwen, i wen ippuwaââden"
  21,104,"Ass ideg ara Nesnefvas igenni am tweôqep n tira, akken Nebda axlaq amezwaru, ad as Nales. D lemâahda fellane£. Akka, ih, ara Nexdem"
  21,105,"Ni$ Nura deg Ihellilen, deffir usmekti: \"ara iweôten tamurt, d imdanen iW imaânen"
  21,106,"Deg wayagi, war ccekk, d asali i ugdud iâabbaden"
  21,107,"Ur k id Nuzen, siwa d aêunu i imavalen"
  21,108,"Ini: \"iyi d ippuweêêan, siwa: Öebbi nnwen d Öebbi Yiwen kan. Kunwi ma d imvuâen"
  21,109,"Ma wexxôen, ini: \"âaggne$ awen, akken ma tellam; ur éôi$ ma iqôeb, ne$ ibâad, ayen i wen ippuwaââden"
  21,110,"Neppa, s tidep, Issen awal d iff$en, Issen ayen tessusmem"
  21,111,"Ur éôi$ ma, ayagi, ahat d ahewwel nnwen, u d zzhu n tallit kan"
  21,112,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Eêkem s tidep. Mass nne$, Aênin, i nepper d Amâiwen, mgal ayen teppandim"